# {{projectName}}

Generated with [create-faster](https://github.com/plvo/create-faster) using the **Cloudflare Static Site** blueprint — a static Next.js (`output: 'export'`) marketing site with an MDX blog, served as Cloudflare Workers static assets.

## Getting started

```bash
bun install
bun run dev
```

## Build & deploy

```bash
bun run build      # next build → static export in out/
bun run preview    # serve the built assets locally with wrangler
bun run deploy     # next build && wrangler deploy
```

Deploying and pointing a custom domain is documented in [`docs/agents/cloudflare-deploy.md`](docs/agents/cloudflare-deploy.md).

